# 🚀 My Flask App (Dockerized)

This is a simple Python Flask web application containerized using Docker.

## 📦 Features

* Lightweight Python Flask app
* Runs on port 5000
* Beginner-friendly Docker project

## ▶️ How to Run

```bash
docker run -p 5000:5000 mayankchichulkar/my-flask-app
```

Then open:
http://localhost:5000

## 🛠️ Built With

* Python
* Flask
* Docker


